{"tid":95082,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"還有韓妹在台灣遭性侵?韓國外交部:又接到七單舉報","createTime":"2017-01-25T17:51:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T12:18:11.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"89fa7eb1aaf599b9e8599f31c8b7aacd8d244d67","tid":95082,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T17:51:06.000Z","msg":"<strong>還有韓妹在台遭性侵？韓外交部：又接到七起舉報</strong><br />\n2017/01/25 15:12:00<br />\n<br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n繼日前2名韓國女遊客在台北遭計程車司機下藥性侵案後，又有更多韓國女性出面舉報！韓國外交部今天（25日）表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">外交部又接到了7起來自<strong>訪台遊客</strong>的類似舉報。</span><br />\n<br />\n1月12日，2名韓國女遊客在台北遭計程車司機下藥性侵，嫌疑男子正在接受調查。據<strong>《韓聯社》</strong>報導，韓國外交部表示，韓國女性在台灣遭性侵事件發生後，外交部又接到了7起來自訪台遊客的類似舉報，韓方已通過當地機構等要求台方徹查<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n韓國外交部日前（23日）召見台駐韓機構相關人士，抗議日前發生南韓女性在台灣遭性侵事件，要求台灣方面嚴懲並嚴防事件重演。台方表示將在調查結果出爐後即刻告知韓方。<br />\n<br />\nlink:<a href=\"http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=219689\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D219689&d=v5ULw9joTTlZplBFgqv%2BGXvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=f6b16791\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D219689&h=27591e7f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=219689</a>"},{"pid":"37c059ea8d83c66cf67e342efd40b9f656637224","tid":95082,"uid":41245,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T17:55:36.000Z","msg":"7單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新北一個鐘都7單啦<br />\n大驚小怪，抹黑台灣<br />\n樓豬係五毛"},{"pid":"73b21fa0742b0baf40efe2037323fa2491f48e16","tid":95082,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T03:35:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fc7e027f7e03c334555a99d46053ead8c14a046","tid":95082,"uid":41408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T03:45:28.000Z","msg":"又食台妹又食韓妹   屌你呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d218be3000d6115dbfce68faab0a370823705974","tid":95082,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T03:53:38.000Z","msg":"最美的風景<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n祟台：唔係台灣人黎嫁 係支那人扮<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a65e60da8040a1b2392e85488c2ce834c464416","tid":95082,"uid":22633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:02:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>7單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n新北一個鐘都7單啦<br />\n大驚小怪，抹黑台灣<br />\n樓豬係五毛</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nin 新北 we trust<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2200aa2ffe1d8246bc321b450fd63b830a561041","tid":95082,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:49:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c005bc49ccca1b5c0f86d03f503e47790389ca60","tid":95082,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:50:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://blog.sina.com.tw/myimages/245/5621/images/20130519010433104.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.sina.com.tw%2Fmyimages%2F245%2F5621%2Fimages%2F20130519010433104.jpg&h=ed799b67&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28f35e7d075c9414b363416263ca03ee404bf1cc","tid":95082,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T09:54:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"http://blog.sina.com.tw/myimages/245/5621/images/20130519010433104.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fblog.sina.com.tw%2Fmyimages%2F245%2F